item.title: [HIVE-6671] WebHCat Job Submission API 'enablelog' parameter is only supported with Hadoop 1
item.description: We should throw a consistent exception if enablelog=true and WebHCat is talking to H2
item.summary: WebHCat Job Submission API 'enablelog' parameter is only supported with Hadoop 1
